-- site-doc.header: Points:

1.Do not apply a stroke to the logo

2.Do not recolor any part of the logo

3.Do not apply drop shadow or effects to the logo

4.Do not rotate the logo in any way

5.Do not distort the logo in any way

6.Do not use the logo as a framing device for imagery

